# Cursor Rules for ISHARAPAL Project

## File Creation Rules

**CRITICAL: Do NOT create any .md (Markdown) files in this repository.**

- Never create new .md files unless explicitly requested by the user
- Do not create documentation files, README files, or any markdown files
- If documentation is needed, use .txt files instead
- Existing .md files should not be modified unless explicitly requested

